&lt;li&gt;Transaction posting and reversals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-currency transaction handling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automated recurring entries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Budget vs. actual reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Financial statement generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
